{"tid":1875029,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國政府考慮將系統大規模遷入Linux，來替代Windows 7的到期","createTime":"2020-02-11T13:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T10:02:40.000Z","uid":1086,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f63ec1a1c1f3c9a8118ede10372bbe9dc96e3a25","tid":1875029,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:56:59.000Z","msg":"來自微軟官方網站信息顯示，對Win7等系統終止支持後，用戶電腦仍然可以繼續工作，但是(微軟官方)將不再提供任何問題的技術支持、軟件更新、安全更新或修復等服務。 微軟提醒用戶，&ldquo;如果沒有持續軟件和安全更新，電腦遭受病毒和惡意軟件攻擊的風險會更大。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，韓國政府計劃在2026年完成向Linux系統的遷移工作，屆時Linux將會成為網絡訪問的主要設備。 據悉，韓國郵政服務將從Windows 7遷移到TMaxOS，這是由韓國軟件公司TmaxSoft支持的基於Linux的操作系統，該發行版本是由韓國本地公司開發的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com//tmp/phpGUjc8U.webp/bigjpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F%2Ftmp%2FphpGUjc8U.webp%2Fbigjpg&h=8620d5db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n据了解，韩国国防部已经使用Harmonica OS系统则是基于Ubuntu 18.04 LTS，TMAX OS系统则将在邮政服务部门使用。2026年之前，韩国公共行政和安全部计划将所有公共机构和地方政府完全采用Open OS。韩国政府各部委和机构的目标是取代Windows操作系统，进而摆脱对微软公司的依赖。"},{"pid":"5b59b982bee483de12151bc2e6887f9074dea64d","tid":1875029,"uid":2192,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:39:37.000Z","msg":"唔好搞咁多野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4286cb767c19f6efee865c141f70f920f03b4363","tid":1875029,"uid":12628,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:42:20.000Z","msg":"Mr.A 好快入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe1e32b0f4151461137f3d48c61e41a2152d2a7","tid":1875029,"uid":59976,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:46:52.000Z","msg":"德國表示笑而不語"},{"pid":"dc3c3de7f47f78703b26ef614b585a7a6f6e4096","tid":1875029,"uid":21699,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:33:04.000Z","m